NAME
	account

SYNOPSYS
	account [-g] <name>

DESCRIPTION
	Allows an archwizard to check the GoG bank account of a player.
	It will display the coins account of the player in two columns.
	The first column contains the actual account value and the second
	the coins in the minimized version.

ARGUMENTS
	-g	Display also the gems stored at the various deposits.
	<name>	The name of the player.
